snippet.title: Discovery + Presents “JOHNNY vs AMBER,” 2 Episode Documentary ft. Johnny Depp & Amber Heard Conflict
snippet.description:
Discovery has commissioned “Johnny vs Amber,” a two-episode documentary that tells the story of the breakdown of Johnny Depp and Amber Heard’s relationship.

This documentary claims it will be showcasing both sides, but we will see about that this fall.

Read more about it here: https://variety.com/2021/tv/news/johnny-depp-amber-heard-documentary-discovery-1235115878/?fbclid=IwAR1VmkEesZSnxh8JJTIHCn7ckl4N_nfcEbMHKHj5AiB28X8xTBW-d9_eQ9o
